caller_intent: The caller (Jessica Gregory from Lions Insurance) intended to follow up on a windshield replacement service to ensure it was completed successfully.
resolution_steps: Automated voicemail system informed caller of unavailability and requested name/number for callback.
Caller left a voicemail message to check on the service and provided contact information.
summary: An outbound call from Lions Insurance left a voicemail to follow up on a windshield replacement. The recipient's voicemail system was activated, and no direct conversation occurred.
